          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our story isn’t just about rugs; it’s about a legacy of creativity and resilience passed down through generations. It began with my great-grandfather, who crafted the finest Persian rug in Iran and earned our family the honor of using the royal crown as our crest.My grandfather continued that tradition, not only as a master of his craft but as someone who gave back to his community, building schools and hospitals.</p>",
