          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The journey was tough. I had to build the technology from scratch, test hundreds of materials, and just as we were ready to launch, the COVID-19 pandemic hit.</p><p>We had to let go of team members, and I found myself working alone on cold nights, trying to figure out how to pivot.</p><p>It was during those challenging times that I realized I needed to bring in a partner who could help me refine and return to the original vision.</p><p>That partner was Mason, someone with a background in advertising and fashion, who knew how to blend art and business.</p>",
